data.description: DRASTIC PRICE ADJUSTMENT. Seller has moved out and wants to sell. Quaint cottage-type home in Waccasassa just 5 miles west of Newberry. Very low Gilchrist County property taxes. Fully fenced yard on corner lot with established orange and grapefruit trees. Two-car garage with attached carport and shed. This home has been loved and needs some renovation, including paint and flooring. The location is convenient for a short commute to Gainesville and the University of Florida, yet surrounded by natural old Florida. The best of both worlds. Interior photos will be available by Nov. 24 but don't hesitate to take a look for yourself now.
